    "headline": "Texas sues Netflix over data collection; shares edge lower",
    "summary": "Investing.com -- Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton has filed a lawsuit against Netflix Inc (NASDAQ:NFLX), alleging the streaming giant illegally surveilled users and exploited children’s data. The legal action claims the company rebranded itself as a \"logging company\" that prioritizes data monetization over consumer privacy. The state’s petition alleges that Netflix deceptively collected sensitive behavioral information without obtaining proper consent from its millions of Texas subscribers. Sha",
